the audience and people do it.

00:06:08.819 --> 00:06:11.500
So can you read it for
yourselves in the back there?

00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:15.329
We'll parse it a little bit.
 

00:06:15.329 --> 00:06:25.300
 
 

00:06:25.300 --> 00:06:28.415
"Civilization which no
brain has designed but which has

00:06:28.415 --> 00:06:31.689
