Prof: Okay,

00:15:27.746 --> 00:15:32.509
what you would begin doing is
reaching out to others.

00:15:32.509 --> 00:15:37.808
You would probably have to
reach out to several others,

00:15:37.808 --> 00:15:42.097
and those others--the others
who actually make these

00:15:42.097 --> 00:15:45.421
toothbrushes are--
do you suppose those plants are

00:15:45.421 --> 00:15:46.639
