combining many small pieces of

00:18:50.865 --> 00:18:58.839
engineering from other fields,
and by using a moving conveyor

00:18:58.839 --> 00:19:01.720
belt,
which carried the car along,

00:19:01.720 --> 00:19:04.548
and workers who stayed in
position,

00:19:04.548 --> 00:19:08.020
