00:23:16.660 --> 00:23:20.528
Do you think she knows what we
do in here?

00:23:20.528 --> 00:23:25.430
She would only know if I were
in a lot of trouble,

00:23:25.430 --> 00:23:26.828
or you were.
 

00:23:26.828 --> 00:23:32.358
There are hundreds of courses,
even thousands,

00:23:32.358 --> 00:23:38.690
and the dispersion of agency,
the--last summer I sat at my

00:23:38.690 --> 00:23:45.798
summer house in Northern Vermont
with a stack of books about that

00:23:45.798 --> 00:23:48.095
high,
picking the books for this

00:23:48.095 --> 00:23:48.460
course.
 

00:23:48.460 --> 00:23:52.660
She didn't supervise that;
