small assets into a smaller

00:46:03.871 --> 00:46:09.545
number of big assets,
so too can capital be formed in

00:46:09.545 --> 00:46:15.864
poor countries by formalizing
property and allowing people to

00:46:15.864 --> 00:46:22.184
make investments by taking on
debt which is secured by formal

00:46:22.184 --> 00:46:23.659
property.
 

00:46:23.659 --> 00:46:28.762
